al space event in the Golden City" "<img src=\"http://www.esa.int/images/prague_small,1.jpg\"  align=\"right\" /> This month the annual Congress of the International Astronautical Federation (IAF) will be held in Prague for the first time in 33 years. The global event highlights the growing activities in space industry, science and education in the Czech Republic — ESA's newest Member State." "http://www.esa.int/esaCP/SEMWQJEODDG_index_0.html" (19589 61696) new 57 nil nil ((title nil "Global space event in the Golden City") (description nil "   <img src=\"http://www.esa.int/images/prague_small,1.jpg\"  align=\"right\" /> This month the annual Congress of the International Astronautical Federation (IAF) will be held in Prague for the first time in 33 years. The global event highlights the growing activities in space industry, science and education in the Czech Republic — ESA's newest Member State. ") (link nil "http://www.esa.int/esaCP/SEMWQJEODDG_index_0.html") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "SEMWQJEODDG") (pubDate nil "Tue, 7 Sep 2010 09:00:00 +0100"))) ("Mars500 video diary 7 - Preparing the meals (with a shaker)" "<img src=\"http://www.esa.int/images/ss_S,1036.jpg\"  align=\"right\" /> The Mars500 crew has more than 450 days to go and three times as many main meals to prepare. To avoid monotony, they innovate new ways to prepare food: Diego is using a very expensive machine to make smoothies." "http://www.esa.int/esaHS/SEMSOVVO1FG_index_0.html" (19588 40832) new 58 nil nil ((title nil "Mars500 video diary 7 - Preparing the meals (with a shaker)") (description nil "   <img src=\"http://www.esa.int/images/ss_S,1036.jpg\"  align=\"right\" /> The Mars500 crew has more than 450 days to go and three times as many main meals to prepare. To avoid monotony, they innovate new ways to prepare food: Diego is using a very expensive machine to make smoothies. ") (link nil "http://www.esa.int/esaHS/SEMSOVVO1FG_index_0.html") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "SEMSOVVO1FG") (pubD